oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Differential Diagnosis of CNS Problems
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Edwards, Alvin J.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Many of you were present today at our seminar when we talked about BVD in cattle. We spent the entire day talking about the problems of BVD and the losses that were incurred from it. I am sure you will recognize that we never did mention the severe losses from CNS - Central Nervous System Disorders. Well, that is the topic we will cover now the differential diagnosis of central nervous system disorders in cattle.
